I"{<p>Welcome to Classical Field Theory, a subject which is severely undertaught in undergraduate and graduate physics programs.</p>

<p><a class="page-link" href="/classical-ft/introduction"> Introduction - What is Classical Field Theory? </a></p>

<p>The prerequisites are as follows</p>
<ol>
  <li>An excellent background in electromagnetic theory</li>
  <li>A working knowledge of continuum mechanics (fluid mechanics and elasticity)</li>
  <li>A working knowledge of multivariable and vector calculus</li>
  <li>A working knowledge of complex analysis</li>
</ol>

